@host = http://localhost:5239
@json = application/json

### Listar contactos
GET {{host}}/api/contacts
Accept: {{json}}

### Obtener contacto por ID
GET {{host}}/api/contacts/1
Accept: {{json}}

### Crear contacto
POST {{host}}/api/contacts
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace",
  "email": "ada@example.com",
  "isFavorite": false
}

### Actualizar contacto
PUT {{host}}/api/contacts/1
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace",
  "email": "ada@newmail.com",
  "isFavorite": true
}

### Marcar como favorito
PATCH {{host}}/api/contacts/1/favorite?value=true

### Quitar de favoritos
PATCH {{host}}/api/contacts/1/favorite?value=false

### Eliminar contacto
DELETE {{host}}/api/contacts/1

